params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.tenant
params.description: Required. Resource name of tenant the completion is performed within. The format is "projects/{project_id}/tenants/{tenant_id}", for example, "projects/foo/tenants/bar".

params.name: data.query
params.description: Required. The query used to generate suggestions. The maximum number of allowed characters is 255.

params.name: data.language_codes
params.description: The list of languages of the query. This is the BCP-47 language code, such as "en-US" or "sr-Latn". For more information, see Tags for Identifying Languages. The maximum number of allowed characters is 255.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Required. Completion result count. The maximum allowed page size is 10.

params.name: data.company
params.description: If provided, restricts completion to specified company. The format is "projects/{project_id}/tenants/{tenant_id}/companies/{company_id}", for example, "projects/foo/tenants/bar/companies/baz".

params.name: data.scope
params.description: The scope of the completion. The defaults is [CompletionScope.PUBLIC][google.cloud.talent.v4.CompleteQueryRequest.CompletionScope.PUBLIC].
